            "actual"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "我們需要專注於實際的情況，而非理論上的推測。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "The actual results differed significantly from the forecast in the quarterly report.",
          "highlight": [
            "actual"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "實際結果與季度報告中的預測有顯著的差異。"
          }
